Developer Terms of Use
des:
Control your robot vacuum through Alexa.

To get started, make sure you install the JETS Home app on your smartphone (Android or iOS) and register a user account. Also make sure your robot vacuum is already connected and configured to your smartphone.

To access the JETS Home skill on Alexa, enter the same user account created in the app when the authentication screen is displayed.

After successful connection, you can define routines like:
• "Alexa, clean house"
• "Alexa, finish cleaning"
